<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lí kāi zhǔ wǒ shén me dōu bù néng zuò 迦南122</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lí kāi zhǔ, wǒ shén me dōu bù néng zuò. lí kāi zhǔ, wǒ yǒng yuǎn dōu shì gàn kě.
 yuàn nǐ wǒ cháng zài zhǔ lǐ miàn, xiàng yī kē shù zāi xī shuǐ páng cháng qīng duō jié guǒ,
 wǒ shǔ yú zhǔ, zhǔ yě shǔ yú wǒ, wǒ yī shēng zài tā de ài zhōng píng ān xǐ lè.
 wǒ shǔ yú zhǔ, zhǔ yě shǔ yú wǒ, wǒ yī shēng zài tā de ài zhōng píng ān xǐ lè.</lyrics>
